COYLE: Swift canine humanoid survivors

The Coyle are an intelligent fox-like humanoid race known for their
speed, cunning, and exceptional physical endurance.  They are natural
survivors with Supernatural Physical Strength and Endurance, and their
keen senses make them valuable scouts and wilderness guides.  Coyle
communities maintain loose tribal structures across wilderness areas.

